item.title: Sina Labbaf
item.description: Bio Name is Sina Labbaf, and my handle is LABOOX. I am a PhD Candidate at UC Irvine. My research is supervised by two amazing Professors Nik Dutt and Amir Rahmani. My main research project is to build services for Health Cybernetics research.
